dear folk:

it's a pleasur to be abl to announc the releas of a new freewar program, 
xavier, an audio and video  extens to interview.

xavier(extens av class for interview) is a c++ class librari
that add multimedia capabl to interview. it allow composit
multimedia object to be built from media object.

specif, it add audio and video object to the class avail
in interview 3.0.1/3.1, and it doe so without chang the
sourc code for the origin class (though sever configur
file for interview need to be chang via a patch file). 
 
current, the xavier audio class ar onli support on sun
workstat with an audio interfac, such as the sparcstat2.

xavier ha been test in the follow environ:

sun:
  machin : sparcserv470 sparcstat-ipc
  os      : sun-os4.1.1 or later
  c++     : sun c++ ver2.1

nec(ew):
  machin : ew4800/210,230
  os      : ew-ux/v(rel4.0) wso41 releas5.1,releas5.2
  c++     : c++ releas3.1

it can be obtain via anonym ftp from 

         interview.stanford.edu in /pub/contrib/
          (xavier.larg-demo.tar, and xavier.tar)

we ar prepar a mail-list for inform regard xavier.
if you ar interest, pleas contact
               
                   xavier@tsl.cl.nec.co.jp. 

i will add your e-mail address to our list.

[refer]
